The steps to adding a new section are as follows

Create a model for the section and export it to mongoose 

Require the routes for the section in the app.js file 

Create a new file in the routes folder and add all of the necessesary routes  

Create a new folder in the views section and add the edit / new / showand index page 

Add the new url to the switch statement in the dashboard javascript file 

ensure the you can easily edit / remove / add a post from the dashboard 

